data.description: Lovely open floor plan 1660 square foot home, 3 bedrooms, spacious main bedroom with huge walk in closet, shower and separate tub, 2 bathroom home. Kitchen island, plenty of storage, open, bright and plenty of room! Spacious back yard, thoughtful landscaping, covered back porch and a raised garden bed area! The home sits on a corner across from open space for a bit of view and that spacious feel! Easy access and minutes from I-17 and just a moment away from downtown Camp Verde!
